expression.expression:
CASE WHEN LOWER(TRIM(a6upmj)) = 'null' OR TRIM(a6upmj) = '' OR TRIM(a6upmj) = '0' THEN NULL 
ELSE 
    to_timestamp(
                substr(
                        CAST(date_add(concat(substr(CAST(CAST(TRIM(a6upmj) AS INT) + 1900000 AS STRING),1,4),'-01-01'), 
                                        CAST(substr(CAST(CAST(TRIM(a6upmj) AS INT) + 1900000 AS string),5,3) AS INT )-1) AS STRING), 1, 10),'yyyy-MM-dd') END
